WEBVTT

00:01.305 --> 00:02.959
Previously on
The Big Bang Theory...

00:03.003 --> 00:07.094
Can you believe our little lamb
is finally getting married?

00:07.137 --> 00:10.010
He can't believe it.

00:10.053 --> 00:12.186
And neither can I.

00:12.229 --> 00:14.405
[laughing]Hi, Dad. How you doing?

00:18.279 --> 00:21.064
[voice breaking]: Then by
the power vested in me...

00:21.108 --> 00:23.327
by
EvenYouCanPerformWeddings.com...

00:25.329 --> 00:27.679
...I now pronounce you
husband and wife.

00:28.245 --> 00:30.204
You may kiss the bride.

00:32.293 --> 00:34.295
[crowd cheering]

00:37.820 --> 00:40.170
Good morning, wife.

00:40.214 --> 00:41.780
[chuckles]

00:41.824 --> 00:44.435
Good morning, husband.

00:44.479 --> 00:47.090
I can't believe
we're actually married.

00:47.134 --> 00:49.092
It's official.
According to tradition,

00:49.136 --> 00:50.615
we should hang
the bedsheets outside

00:50.659 --> 00:54.010
so the villagers can see
that we consummated.

00:54.054 --> 00:55.751
I don't think that
that's appropriate,

00:55.794 --> 00:58.101
considering where we're
starting our honeymoon.

00:58.145 --> 01:00.147
Well, I suppose you're right.

01:02.801 --> 01:04.673
Although,
when you think about it,

01:04.716 --> 01:07.719
Lego is the perfect metaphor
for marital congress.

01:07.763 --> 01:11.984
Two pieces that interlock
with a satisfying snap.

01:12.028 --> 01:16.337
Oh, that'sthe sound
you were making.

01:16.380 --> 01:17.642
Oh, I almost forgot.

01:17.686 --> 01:20.776
While you were sleeping,
I ordered room service.

01:20.819 --> 01:22.473
Really?

01:22.517 --> 01:24.214
Voilà!

01:26.086 --> 01:28.131
You thought it was going
to be food, didn't you?

01:29.524 --> 01:33.136
♪ Our whole universe
was in a hot, dense state ♪

01:33.180 --> 01:36.400
♪ Then nearly 14 billion years
ago expansion started... Wait! ♪

01:36.444 --> 01:38.141
♪ The Earth began to cool

01:38.185 --> 01:40.796
♪ The autotrophs began to drool,
Neanderthals developed tools ♪

01:40.839 --> 01:43.277
♪ We built the Wall ♪ We built the pyramids♪

01:43.320 --> 01:46.018
